  "title": "Purchasing Clerk",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Preparation of Purchase Order/Delivery order/Invoices.</li><li>Provide day-to-day administrative support to the office and Attending to calls.</li><li>Preparing purchase orders and liaising with suppliers in regards to orders and returns.</li><li>Other ad-hoc duties assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements </strong></p><ul><li>Singaporean</li><li>Min.GCE’O’/ITE or equivalent and with/without experience</li><li>Ms Word and Ms Excel</li><li>Bilingual in English / Mandarin.</li><li>Working Hour: 8.00am to 5.00pm (Mon-Fri)/ 8.00am to 12.00pm (Sat)</li></ul><p>Interested candidates, please send in your CV to elecoservices@singnet.com.sg or 6442 3948 (Mon-Fri) </p><p>for an interview.</p>",
